Sure! Here are some job titles that are more specifically focused on either pre-sales or sales engineering roles:

Pre-Sales Engineer:

1. Pre-Sales Solutions Engineer
2. Technical Pre-Sales Consultant
3. Pre-Sales Technical Specialist
4. Pre-Sales Cloud Architect
5. Pre-Sales Support Engineer

Sales Engineer:

2. Technical Sales Consultant
3. Sales Technical Specialist
4. Sales Cloud Architect
5. Sales Support Engineer
